snippet.title: Pocket Mini Golf | Gameplay Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
t’s time for some fun mini-golf! Sit back, relax, and score some holes. Fancy some multiplayer with friends? We've got you covered - up to 4 players on one console!
